{"tid":882534,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏]【三招救市】中證監：會減少不必要干預","createTime":"2018-10-30T07:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:31:20.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"900d5bff6a13e15722caf5cfe27cb34dc9f93179","tid":882534,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=325463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325463&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3b8b9877\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325463&h=d4f22259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=325463</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中證監提出三招救市，內地股市反覆上升，其中，上證綜合指數曾升逾1%。<br />\n<br />\n將進行大額回購的平保A股升3%，券商股亦有追捧，個別更升停板。另外，傳內地汽車購置稅減少，汽車零部件概念股急炒上。<br />\n<br />\n中證監表示，會加快提升上市公司質量、優化交易監管，以及鼓勵價值投資三方面工作。<br />\n<br />\n其中，在鼓勵價值投資方面，中證監指，會減少不必要干預，讓市場對監管有明確預期，讓投資者有公平交易機會，鼓勵價值投資，引導更多中長期資金進入市場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵價值投資 洗鳩你腦, 隻隻都咁靚, 唔買就笨柒<br />\n<br />\n數學提, 100點先跌1% = 99點, 咁99點升反1% 有99.99, 咁係未完成國家交托既托市任務呢, 嘩屌再贏"},{"pid":"1e1d6358e8aa99e160773eb58c33592d3fc94fbf","tid":882534,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"外資走晒 , 市民啲錢責晒去樓市 , 邊個仲有錢買?"},{"pid":"a41c16b809fb680a48c2cc63af246604475c7a59","tid":882534,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"做乜撚成9日救市救市<br />\n市場真係要咁架咩"},{"pid":"ce26b63002569ebd0bb5f252aa693883051a8f76","tid":882534,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e1d6358e8aa99e160773eb58c33592d3fc94fbf","tid":882534,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"外資走晒 , 市民啲錢責晒去樓市 , 邊個仲有錢買?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"銀行借錢比